    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the juice of <strong>half</strong> the <strong>lime[s]</strong> to a small bowl with your <strong>chilli relish</strong>, <strong>chopped ginger</strong>,<strong> sriracha</strong> (can’t handle the heat? Go easy!) and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp]</span> <strong>water</strong></p><p>Stir it all together – this is your <strong>sweet chilli sauce</strong></p><p>Cut the<strong> remaining lime</strong> into 1 wedge</p>",
